52 TEST(Property, reset) {
53  PropertyMap props;
54  props.declare<double>("double1");
55 
56  // setCurrent() only assigns temporary values
57  props.setCurrent("double1", 1.0);
58  ASSERT_EQ(props.get<double>("double1"), 1.0);
59  EXPECT_TRUE(props.property("double1").defaultValue().empty());
60 
61  // they can be reset to their defaults
62  props.reset();
63  EXPECT_FALSE(props.property("double1").defined());
64 
65  // set() also updates the default
66  props.set("double1", 1.0);
67  EXPECT_EQ(props.get<double>("double1"), 1.0);
68  EXPECT_EQ(boost::any_cast<double>(props.property("double1").defaultValue()), 1.0);
69 
70  props.setCurrent("double1", 2.0);
71  EXPECT_EQ(props.get<double>("double1"), 2.0);
72  EXPECT_EQ(boost::any_cast<double>(props.property("double1").defaultValue()), 1.0);
73 
74  // back to default
75  props.reset();
76  EXPECT_EQ(props.get<double>("double1"), 1.0);
